{"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"instancetype"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"cameraLookingAtCenterCoordinate:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationCoordinate2D","preciseIdentifier":"c:@S@CLLocationCoordinate2D"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"centerCoordinate"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"altitude:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationDistance","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDistance"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"altitude"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"pitch:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CGFloat","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CGFloat"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"pitch"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"heading:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"CLLocationDirection","preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@CLLocationDirection"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"heading"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The geographic coordinate on which the map should be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"centered."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"centerCoordinate"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The altitude (measured in meters) above the map at which the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"camera should be situated. The altitude may be less than the distance from"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the camera’s viewpoint to the camera’s focus point."}]}],"name":"altitude"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text